name: Tangie Land
description: Tangie Land is a hybrid weed strain made from a genetic cross between Tangie and Candyland. This strain is 50% sativa and 50% indica. Tangie Land is 18.5% THC, making this strain an ideal choice for experienced cannabis consumers. Bred by unknown breeders, the average price of Tangie Land typically ranges from $10-$15 per gram.
